metadata.name: Dark Geometry
metadata.description: "This NFT you see kind of symbolizes life. Strangely enough, the emotions we express are not the same as the emotions we experience. There may be different thoughts in the depths of the emotions we experience." If you look carefully, the icons outside and inside do not rotate the same. If you look more carefully, 1. and you may notice that the 3rd and the 2nd and 4th rotate to the same side.
